<li><a href="http://news.xinhuanet.com/talking/2015-01/22/c_1114093071.htm" target="_blank"><img src="../titlepic/111597/1115976796_1438304778309_title0h.gif" width="380" height="195" border="0" alt="第一届&ldquo;寻找百姓生命保护神&rdquo;活动" /></a></li>
